reviewText: Got this product and I thought that it was going to be another expensive buy but boy it is worth it. I am a little bit older and a couch potato and this really helps me with my exercises.  I want to create my own home gym and having these kind of exercise equipment are so handy and compact.  I suggest that if you an find out to go ahead and get it.  I am so surprise that this did not create a great following because it's a great workout system and equipment.
